content: Nolitusne: You don't see it as a competition but an agreement? You're quite a peculiar person.
You: This is my race with you and our pact, isn't it? That's why I'm going to try my best to finish it, so you'll feel happy too, right?
Nolitusne: Hahahaha you're right, so maybe I'll be convinced even if I lose to you later.
